Cell["Dynamic Interactivity", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"abd2714b-c40b-491d-9b98-1f3d249655e3"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Learning Objectives", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"a97f34a4-babe-4547-8f90-f67ece348d5f"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Adding clickable interactivity to plot elements", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"ad5771a2-c550-4552-a8f2-c61598f6ccc4"],

Cell["\<\
Dynamic onscreen real estate is valuable. Organizing information within \
interactive elements like buttons and tabs can provide easier access to \
additional data. This module demonstrates how to add basic interactive \
features, such as:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2fbacd79-9a2d-4e71-8556-7b8146eb7163"],

